{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">了解热敏电阻工作原理。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">NTC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">型热敏电阻随温度的增加阻值变小。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"器材","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">学生电源、开关、滑动变阻器、蜂鸣器、热敏电阻</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">1.闭合开关；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">2.调高热水温度；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">3.注意蜂鸣器的发声情况；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">4.调低热水温度；</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">5.注意蜂鸣器的发声情况。</span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"结论","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">温度超过</span>50<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">℃时蜂鸣器发声，低于</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">℃时蜂鸣器不发声。</span></span></span></span></p>"},{"title":"补充","data":"<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">NTC<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">型热敏电阻随温度的增加阻值变小；</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:28px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri\">PTC</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">型热敏电阻随温度的增加阻值变大。</span></span></span></span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600}